UNITED STATES v. OIL SEEDS PRESSING CO. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. February 2, 1903.) No. 91. Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. J. Frank Lloyd, for the United States.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

No opinion. Affirmed in open court. See (C. C.) 114 Fed. 793.
